title: How to Use Web Crawlers for SEO
excerpt: Web crawler tools are essential for search engine optimization, but the info they provide can be overwhelming. Here's how to prioritize and cut through the clutter.

title: SEO How-to, Part 9: Diagnosing Crawler Issues
excerpt: Search engines must crawl and index your site before it can rank in organic search. Thus optimizing your content is pointless if search engines cannot access it. This is the ninth installment in my “SEO How-to” series.
